<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #2c3e50; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; border-top: 6px solid #27ae60; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
    
    /* Die Ziel-Person Karte */
    .target-card { background-color: #f1f8e9; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; margin: 25px 0; border: 2px dashed #a5d6a7; }
    .target-label { font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7f8c8d; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    .target-name { font-size: 28px; color: #2e7d32; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0; }
    
    .info-grid { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #555; background: #fafafa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #ccc; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="" style="display:none;">

    <h2 style="text-align: center; color: #2c3e50;">ü§´ Die Auslosung ist vollendet!</h2>
    
    <p>Hallo {{guestName}},</p>
    
    <p>Das Event <strong>{{eventName}}</strong> von {{hostName}} r√ºckt n√§her. Der Zufallsgenerator hat entschieden!</p>
    
    <p>Du bist der Wichtel ("Secret Santa") f√ºr:</p>
    
    <div class="target-card">
      <div class="target-label">Dein Ziel ist</div>
      <div class="target-name">{{assignment.recipientName}}</div>
      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666;">(Pssst... verrate es niemandem!)</p>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Zur Erinnerung:</strong></p>
    
    {{#if eventDescription}}
    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #777; margin-top: 20px;">
      <em>Hinweis zum Event: "{{eventDescription}}"</em>
    </p>
    {{/if}}

    <ul>
      <li>Das Geschenk sollte ca. <strong>{{budget}}</strong> kosten.</li>
      <li>Bitte bringe es verpackt am <strong>{{eventDate}}</strong> mit.</li>
      <li>Verrate niemandem, wen du gezogen hast!</li>
    </ul>


    <p style="margin-top: 25px; text-align: center;">Viel Spa√ü beim Schenken!</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Einladung verwaltet von {{hostName}} via Tadaa.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
